Driver training programs range from one-day orientations to multi-week certification processes. Comprehensive training covers defensive driving techniques, passenger interaction protocols, emergency response procedures, and vehicle-specific operational characteristics. Mountain driving training becomes crucial for Colorado operations because techniques for handling large vehicles on steep grades and in winter conditions aren't intuitive.

